### Q.2 Daily Average Points for Each User
*Calculate the daily average points for each user.*

**SQL Query:**
```sql
SELECT 
    username, 
    DATE(submitted_at) AS submission_date, 
    AVG(points) AS daily_avg_points
FROM user_submissions
GROUP BY username, submission_date
ORDER BY submission_date DESC, username ASC;
